title: Plagarism
info:
Plagarism
By Fearofdark
Finished: 29th August 2009

A song to express my fustraition at this present time. Oddly, inspired by the Po
kemon
Platinum battle scene against one of the legendary pokemon (no mocking, it's a g
ood game!)

You know who you are...oh, and enjoy!

(also, my first chiptune that doesn't really use any guitar or synth samples:) T
he strings
